        {{#if hasInternalInput}} mutatingPreResolve?: (hook: {{#if hasInternalInput}}HookRequestWithInput<Injected{{name}}Input>{{else}}HookRequest{{/if}}) => Promise<Injected{{name}}Input>;{{/if}}
